====''Pokémon the Series''====
{{main|Dawn (anime)}}
{{main|Alternate World Dawn}}
Dawn is one of the many [[player character]]s appearing in the games to also be present in {{aniseries|PTS}}. Appearing throughout {{aniseries|DP}}, she is a [[Pokémon Coordinator]] and a former {{ashfr|traveling companion}} of {{Ash}} and {{an|Brock}}. She reappeared in {{aniseries|BW}} and {{aniseries|JN}}.

In ''[[JN089|The Gates of Warp!]]'', an {{pkmn|multiverse|alternate universe}} version of Dawn was introduced. Unlike the main universe Dawn, this version is a talented Trainer who has participated in the [[Sinnoh League]].
